trans-unit.source: Specifies a property or a field to be extracted from an activity and sent to the tracking service together with an associated collection of annotations when a track point is matched.
trans-unit.target: Angir en egenskap eller et felt som er hentet fra en aktivitet og sendes til Sporingstjenesten sammen med en tilknyttet samling av merknader når et Sporingspunkt samsvarer.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] Each user event or activity status event that occurs during a workflow instance is associated with a specific activity.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Hver bruker hendelse eller status aktivitetshendelse som forekommer i løpet av en arbeidsflytforekomst som er knyttet til en bestemt aktivitet.

trans-unit.source: An ActivityDataTrackingExtract specifies a property or a field to be extracted from this activity.
trans-unit.target: En ActivityDataTrackingExtract angir en egenskap eller et felt som skal trekkes ut denne aktiviteten.

trans-unit.source: You can include an ActivityDataTrackingExtract in either <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName> to instruct the runtime tracking infrastructure to extract a field or a property from the associated activity when the infrastructure matches an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> or a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>.
trans-unit.target: Du kan inkludere en ActivityDataTrackingExtract i enten <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eller for <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>å be kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur for å hente et felt eller en egenskap fra den tilhørende aktiviteten når infrastrukturen samsvarer med en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>eller <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The runtime tracking infrastructure puts the extracted data and any associated annotations in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> or the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord> that it returns to the tracking service.
trans-unit.target: Kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur plasserer utpakkede dataene, og eventuelle tilknyttede kommentarer i den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>eller <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord>som returneres til Sporingstjenesten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>

trans-unit.source: Set <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> to specify the field or property for the runtime tracking infrastructure to extract from the activity.
trans-unit.target: Angi <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A>til å angi feltet eller egenskapen for kjøring sporing infrastrukturen ikke trekke ut fra aktiviteten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can associate additional information with the extracted data by adding to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Annotations%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Du kan knytte tilleggsinformasjon til utpakkede dataene ved å legge til <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Annotations%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Annotations%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: If you use this constructor you must explicitly set <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> to a value different from a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic) elsewhere in your code.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du bruker denne konstruktøren må du eksplisitt angi <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A>til en verdi som er forskjellig fra et nullreferanse (`Nothing` i Visual Basic) sted i koden.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract"></xref> class by using the specified activity member name.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract"> </xref> klassen ved hjelp av det angitte aktivitet medlemsnavnet.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> is initialized to `member`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A>initialiseres til `member`.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A>

trans-unit.source: The dot delineated name of the field or the property that should be extracted and sent to the tracking service.
trans-unit.target: Punktet merket navnet på feltet eller egenskapen som skal trekkes ut og sendt til Sporingstjenesten.

trans-unit.source: member is a null reference ( in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: memberer en nullreferanse ( i Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of annotations associated with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Henter samlingen av merknader tilknyttet utpakkede dataene.

trans-unit.source: When a track point is matched, the runtime tracking infrastructure includes both the extracted data and the annotation collection in the tracking record that it sends to the tracking service.
trans-unit.target: Når et Sporingspunkt samsvarte, inkluderer runtime sporing infrastruktur både utpakkede dataene og merknadssamlingen i sporing oppføringen som sendes til Sporingstjenesten.

trans-unit.source: You can add to Annotations to associate additional information with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Du kan legge til merknader for å knytte tilleggsinformasjon til utpakkede dataene.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"></xref> associated with the activity property or field to be extracted.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"> </xref> tilknyttet aktiviteten egenskap eller felt som skal trekkes ut.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er en tom samling.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the field or the property to be extracted from the associated activity when a track point is matched.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir feltet eller egenskapen som skal trekkes ut fra den tilhørende aktiviteten når et Sporingspunkt samsvarer.

trans-unit.source: Member can be set to specify a field or property of the activity; a member of such a field or property; or a single element of a field or property (or a member of either) that implements the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface.
trans-unit.target: Medlemmet kan angis til å angi et felt eller en egenskap for aktivitet. et medlem av slike et felt eller en egenskap. eller ett enkelt element i et felt eller egenskapen (eller et medlem av enten) som implementerer den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>

trans-unit.source: For example, if the activity has a `string` property named MyString and you want the runtime tracking infrastructure to return its length, you can set Member to "MyString.Length".
trans-unit.target: Hvis aktiviteten har for eksempel en `string` egenskapen navnet minString og ønskede kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur for å returnere lengden, kan du angi medlemmet "MyString.Length".

trans-unit.source: Alternatively, to return the second char in MyString, you can set Member to "MyString[1]".
trans-unit.target: For å returnere den andre char i minString, kan du også angi medlemmet "MinString [1]".

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Member must be the real name of a property on the activity type.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Medlem må være reelle navnet på en egenskap for aktivitetstypen.

trans-unit.source: This name may be different from what you see in the designer because the designer supports the ability to localize and map property names.
trans-unit.target: Dette navnet kan være forskjellig fra ser du i designer fordi utformeren støtter muligheten til å localize og tilordne egenskapsnavn.

trans-unit.source: A dot delineated name that specifies a field or a property of the activity.
trans-unit.target: Punktum merket navn som angir et felt eller en egenskap til aktiviteten.

trans-unit.source: The default is a null reference (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""></xref> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Standarden er en nullreferanse (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""> </xref> i Visual Basic).
